data.description: Welcome to your 4-bedroom home with a bonus room for a gym or office! This turn-key property near Pearsall Park and Miller's Pond offers three bathrooms, hassle-free maintenance with no carpet, and recent upgrades, including new shingles (Feb 2024), HVAC serviced (Sep 2023), and a new water heater installation (Sep 2023). Less than 10 minutes from Kelly Air Force Base, it combines convenience and charm.  Schedule your tour today.
